Replace this file with your real exported KeyKing vault.

1. Open the KeyKing desktop app.
2. Go to the Keys tab and add your free provider keys (Groq, Google Gemini, Mistral, etc.).
3. Click Export Vault and save it as "vault.kk".
4. Put that file at api/vault.kk (next to generate.js).

For Vercel deployments, prefer setting the vault contents as an environment variable
named KEYKING_VAULT (paste the full file contents) plus KEYKING_MASTER_PASSWORD.
That keeps secrets out of git.

This placeholder is not a valid vault.
